<br>
It's only described as allowing you to keep your current illusion when zoning, which imo seems very, very lame, if the duration remains fixed at 30 mins or however long illusions last.<br>
<br>
Anybody have this skill or know somebody who has it? If it is actually a perm. illusion I'd be interested but as it's described it sounds like a waste of 3 points, heh. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87709>Master Rubicant D'Luness - Phantasmist</a><BR>
